  [7813] = {
    ["D"] =
    "As with most other fabrics, our stocks of wool are at an all-time low. Our stores are such that we\'d only need sixty pieces of wool from you total; we should be able to reach our goal with the support of others.$B$BA benevolent gift such as wool, might I add, would certainly increase your local standing in the community! If you have the sixty pieces of wool cloth on you and are ready to donate them, I\'m able to take them from you now.",
