    "<Father Montoy makes some strange gestures in the air in front of you.>$B$BBlessed child, while seeking the vestments of the fallen you may also encounter a desecrated loop. Yet I feel it might not be of much use to you in the way that it is.$B$BWere you to find it, return it to me and I will make sure it will be of use to you.",
